eggs with merguez tomatoes poivrons

merguez should be brought up to room temp


3 merguez 4 eggs 1 tomato a bit of poivrons
    2 bouchon huile olive

Cook merguez + olive oil first at low heat (don't over cook them)
    at the end of cooking add small bit of water and close the lid
    
cook poivrons
then add tomatoes, salt pepper and cook for 15 minutes

cook eggs

then offheat, add merguez coup√©s avec cizeaux
cover and let rest for 5 minutes
